Package frc.robot.BreakerLib.subsystem.cores.drivetrain.swerve.modules

Interface BreakerGenericSwerveModule

All Superinterfaces:
BreakerGenericDevice, BreakerPowerManageable, BreakerSelfTestable
All Known Implementing Classes:
BreakerMK4iFalconSwerveModule
public interface BreakerGenericSwerveModule
extends BreakerGenericDevice
Interface for all Swerve Modules to allow for easy interchangeablity, this class is meant to serve as an intermedairy between your swerve hardware and the BreakerSwerveDrive class
